- Roles:

    cmd_role 'role_name' => (
        abbrev  => 1,
        optargs => sub {
        },
    );

    subcmd 'App::foo::bar' => (
        with    => 'role_name',
        optargs => sub {

            # cmd specific
        },
    );

- Do not inherit options from parent commands?

- An Enum type
    opt things => (
        isa     => 'Enum',
        valid   => [qw/one two three/],
        comment => 'only allows set values',
    );

